@*
    Composite component containing all Mythetech message bus providers.
    Add this component once in your main layout to enable:
    - Clipboard copy commands via CopyToClipboard messages
    - Snackbar notifications via AddNotification messages
    - Dialog display via ShowDialog messages

    Usage in App.razor or MainLayout.razor:
    <MythetechProviders />
*@

<ClipboardCommandProvider />
<SnackbarCommandProvider />
<DialogCommandProvider />
